               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>To be <rs id="t17840915-79-punish395" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840915-79-punish395" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840915-79-punish395" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="whipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840915-79-defend919 t17840915-79-punish395"></join>
               whipped
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17840915-79-punish396" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840915-79-punish396" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
